# Project Assets & Visualizations

This directory contains the static images, charts, and diagrams used to document the Instacart Customer Propensity projec.

##Folder Contents

* **customer_behavior_eda.png **:  -- EDA dashboards showing peak purchasing hours, weekly order volume trends, and the distribution of days between user orders.

* **xgboost_feature_importance**: Visualizes the F-scores of the baseline  model, highlighting which features had the most influence on the initial predictions.
* **baseline_confusion_matrix**:  Confidence score of baseline model
* **Baseline_Model_Perfomance**: Evaluation metric of baseline model

* **Tuned_model_feature_importance**: Visualizes the F-scores of the tuned model, highlighting which features had the most influence on the initial predictions.
* **Refined_Model_Perfomance**:  Confidence score of tuned model
* **Tuned_model_confusion_matrix**: Evaluation metric of tuned model


* **Final_Result**: Output table showing the top 10 customer-product combinations and their associated probability of a repeat purchase.



